</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Sandy &amp; Clackamas</strong> are your best bets within a 30 min drive, offering strong winter and summer runs
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Lower Willamette</strong> is ideal for winter shore plunking at Meldrum Bar .
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Columbia River</strong> provides summer options with easy bank access .
    </li>
    <li>
